claims:
1. A battery comprising:
a sulfur-containing cathode;
an anode; and
a separator between the sulfur-containing cathode and the anode, wherein the sulfur-containing cathode has a coating comprising a single-lithium ion conductor;
wherein the single-lithium ion conductor comprises a polymeric lithium salt;
wherein the polymeric lithium salt is a polymer having a polysulfone backbone with pendent lithium bis(trifluoromethanesulfonyl)imide groups.

5. A battery comprising:
a sulfur-containing cathode;
an anode; and
a separator between the sulfur-containing cathode and the anode, wherein the separator has a coating comprising a single-lithium ion conductor;
wherein the single-lithium ion conductor comprises a polymeric lithium salt;
wherein the polymeric lithium salt is a polymer having a polysulfone backbone with pendent lithium bis(trifluoromethanesulfonyl)imide groups.

9. A method of improving cycling stability of a battery having a sulfur-containing cathode, an anode, and a separator between the sulfur-containing cathode and the anode, the method comprising:
applying a coating comprising a single-lithium ion conductor to at least one of the sulfur-containing cathode and the separator;
wherein the single-lithium ion conductor comprises a polymeric lithium salt;
wherein the polymeric lithium salt is a polymer having a polysulfone backbone with pendent lithium bis(trifluoromethanesulfonyl)imide groups.
